description: The chief minister says a vaccine offers "a brighter 2021", but mass vaccination will "take time".
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man vaccine supply 'proportionate to population'
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man vaccine supply 'proportionate to population' - BBC News
maintext: "The most vulnerable groups will be prioritised for the vaccine, ensuring those at the highest risk are the first to benefit from the protection it offers," he added.
